msgid "welcome to the island!"
msgstr "bienvenue sur l'ile !"

msgid "I'm sorry but you can't stay here..."
msgstr "Desole, mais tu ne peux pas rester ici..."

msgid "Why ???"
msgstr "Pourquoi ???"

msgid "Because our island just became infested by slimes."
msgstr "Parce que notre ile vient d'etre infestee par des slimes."

msgid "No worries, I'm a hero, I'll help you!"
msgstr "T'inquiete, je suis un heros, je vais vous aider !"

msgid "What? Really?"
msgstr "Quoi ? Vraiment ?"

msgid "Of course!"
msgstr "Bien sur !"

msgid "Oh thanks a lot!"
msgstr "Oh merci beaucoup !"

msgid "I think the first thing you should do is to find the cave."
msgstr "Je pense que la premiere chose a faire est de trouver la grotte."

msgid "It's where they came out first."
msgstr "C'est de la qu'ils sont sortis au debut."

msgid "Let me take a look then!"
msgstr "Je vais aller voir ca alors !"

msgid "Alright, and if you're a real hero, please kill 5 slimes before coming back to me (use the attack key when the character is near a slime)."
msgstr "D'accord, et si tu es un vrai heros, tue 5 slimes avant de revenir me voir (utilise la touche d'attaque quand ton personnage est pres d'un slime)."

msgid "Alright, I'll do my best no worry."
msgstr "D'accord, je vais faire de mon mieux."

msgid "Thanks a lot, then see you soon I guess! Do your best hero!!!!"
msgstr "Merci beaucoup, a tres bientot j'espere ! Donne tout, heros !!!!"

msgid "Welcome back hero!"
msgstr "Te revoila, heros !"

msgid "So you didn't lie, you killed 5 slimes only with your sword! That's sounds really amazing and I'm gonna tell your story to all peoples I know..."
msgstr "Donc tu ne mentais pas, tu as tue 5 slimes avec seulement ton epee ! C'est vraiment incroyable, je vais raconter ton histoire a tout le monde..."

msgid "I really had the chance to meet a hero... woah"
msgstr "J'ai vraiment eu de la chance de rencontrer un heros... woah"

msgid "Well sorry lol, you can now continue your adventure in the next island!"
msgstr "Bon desole lol, tu peux maintenant continuer ton aventure vers l'ile suivante !"

msgid "Next island will be the main city, it's now still in build but you may can take a look to files, few things are already here!"
msgstr "La prochaine ile sera la ville principale. Elle est encore en construction, mais tu peux deja aller jeter un coup d'oeil !"

msgid "See you soon hero!"
msgstr "A bientot, heros !"

